Dum Dum Song Lyrics – Asees Kaur | Jacqueline Fernandez

The Dum Dum Song is a vibrant Hindi song sung by Asees Kaur, Bunny, Sagar, Faiz, and Hunny and video featuring Jacqueline Fernandez. Composed by Jaani and Bunny with lyrics by Jaani, the song brings an energetic vibe and catchy beats. Directed by the duo Piyush-Shazia.
